---
title: Early Summer Potato Salad with Crispy Tofu, Dill & Tangy Dijon Dressing
description: Hold onto your hats, people: this is not your ordinary potato salad. Beefed up with crispy tofu, tender green beans, crunchy cucumber, and sautéed leek, you may never look at potato salad the same way again. Lemony dill is the pièce de résistance - don't be skimpy!
